OL,6,FETAs, which cost #10, are currently
OL,7,Fonly required for nationals of Qatar,
OL,8,FBahrain, Kuwait, Oman, the United Arab
OL,9,FEmirates, Saudi Arabia and Jordan.
OL,11,FThe programme is scheduled to be
OL,12,Fextended to include the European
OL,13,FUnion, the European Economic Area and
OL,14,FSwiss nationals in early 2025, and the
OL,15,Frest of the world this autumn.
OL,17,FMeanwhile the Government has also
OL,18,Frefused calls to reverse the 2020
OL,19,Fdecision to end tax-free shopping for
OL,20,Finbound visitors.
