OL,3,CHeathrow accuses Government of
OL,4,C'curtailing UK's global connectivity'
OL,6,FHeathrow said in a statement: "Current
OL,7,FGovernment policy is curtailing the
OL,8,FUK's global connectivity.
OL,10,F"Initiatives like the introduction of
OL,11,Funnecessary visas for transiting
OL,12,Fpassengers, the absence of tax-free
OL,13,Fshopping and the recently proposed
OL,14,Fhike in business rates underscore the
OL,15,Fneed for ministers to take a cross-
OL,16,Fgovernment approach to policymaking
OL,17,Fthat supports UK aviation's global
OL,18,Fcompetitiveness."
