OL,6,FHeathrow published figures showing 6.7
OL,7,Fmillion passengers travelled through
OL,8,Fthe airport in April, a 4.8% rise on
OL,9,Fthe total of 6.4 million during the
OL,10,Fsame month last year.
OL,12,FHeathrow said this means it is "on
OL,13,Ftrack" for its busiest year for
OL,14,Fpassenger numbers.
OL,16,FDouble-digit year-on-year percentage
OL,17,Fgrowth in passengers was recorded last
OL,18,Fmonth for routes connecting Heathrow
OL,19,Fwith the rest of the UK as well as the
OL,20,FAsia/Pacific and Middle East regions.
