OL,6,FFriday April 19 was Heathrow's busiest
OL,7,Fday for flights since October 2019,
OL,8,Fwith 1,337 taking off or landing.
OL,10,FHeathrow chief executive Thomas
OL,11,FWoldbye said: "It takes an
OL,12,Fextraordinary team to deliver this
OL,13,Fstrong performance and I'm proud of
OL,14,Fwhat everyone across the airport has
OL,15,Fachieved so far this year.
