OL,3,CHeathrow accuses Government of
OL,4,C'curtailing UK's global connectivity'
OL,6,F"As we continue to grow, our focus is
OL,7,Fon making Heathrow fit for the future,
OL,8,Fdelivering reliable journeys for all
OL,9,Four customers today and getting ready
OL,10,Ffor the challenges and opportunities
OL,11,Fof tomorrow.
OL,13,F"But to unlock our full potential to
OL,14,Fhelp grow the country's economy, we
OL,15,Fneed the Government to implement
OL,16,Fpolicies that support UK aviation's
OL,17,Fability to compete globally, and thus
OL,18,Fmake the UK more competitive overall."
